org.gbif.api.model.occurrence

Class DownloadRequest

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.gbif.api.model.occurrence.DownloadRequest

  • public class DownloadRequest
extends Object
    Represents a request to download occurrence records. A download request with a null predicate is interpreted as a "download all" request.
